    "Secondly, in the context of knowledge distillation, we employed the Realtoxicityprompts dataset.",
    "The utilization of this particular dataset may impose limitations on the model's ability to handle a diverse range of malicious query inputs.",
    "To address this limitation, we introduce the Jigsaw dataset in RQ2.",
    "This strategic integration is aimed at enhancing the model's adaptability across a broader spectrum of data types, thus fortifying its capabilities in processing various forms of malicious content.",
